<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Code de vérification AlertProche</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; background: #0a0f1e; color: #e8eaf6; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px; }
    .card {
      background: #131929;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,212,170,0.2);
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    /* Header */
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f1629, #1a2340);
      padding: 32px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,212,170,0.15);
    }
    .logo {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .logo-icon {
      width: 42px; height: 42px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4aa, #007aff);
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    .logo-text {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #e8eaf6;
    }
    .logo-accent { color: #00d4aa; }
    .header-tagline {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #4a5568;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    /* Body */
    .body { padding: 36px 40px; }
    .greeting {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #e8eaf6;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .message {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #8892b0;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    /* Code OTP */
    .otp-container {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0,212,170,0.08), rgba(0,122,255,0.08));
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(0,212,170,0.3);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 24px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .otp-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #00d4aa;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .otp-code {
      font-size: 48px;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: 12px;
      color: #e8eaf6;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4aa, #007aff);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    }
    .otp-expiry {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #4a5568;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .otp-expiry strong { color: #ffb347; }
    /* Info */
    .info-box {
      background: rgba(255,74,74,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,74,74,0.2);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .info-box p {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #8892b0;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .info-box strong { color: #ff6b6b; }
    /* Steps */
    .steps { margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .steps-title {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #8892b0;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .step {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .step-num {
      width: 22px; height: 22px;
      background: rgba(0,212,170,0.15);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,212,170,0.3);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #00d4aa;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 1px;
    }
    .step-text { font-size: 13px; color: #8892b0; line-height: 1.5; }
    /* Footer */
    .footer {
      padding: 20px 40px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer p { font-size: 11px; color: #2d3748; line-height: 1.7; }
    .footer a { color: #00d4aa; text-decoration: none; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="card">

      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">
          <div class="logo-icon">🛡️</div>
          <span class="logo-text">Alert<span class="logo-accent">Proche</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="header-tagline">Plateforme Citoyenne de Protection</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Body -->
      <div class="body">
        <p class="greeting">Bonjour {{pseudo}} 👋</p>
        <p class="message">
          Vous avez demandé à créer un compte sur AlertProche.<br>
          Pour vérifier votre adresse email et sécuriser votre inscription, veuillez utiliser le code ci-dessous.
        </p>

        <!-- Code OTP -->
        <div class="otp-container">
          <div class="otp-label">🔐 Votre code de vérification</div>
          <div class="otp-code">{{code}}</div>
          <div class="otp-expiry">Ce code expire dans <strong>10 minutes</strong></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Étapes -->
        <div class="steps">
          <div class="steps-title">Comment utiliser ce code</div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-num">1</div>
            <div class="step-text">Retournez sur la page d'inscription AlertProche</div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-num">2</div>
            <div class="step-text">Saisissez le code à <strong>5 chiffres</strong> dans le champ prévu</div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-num">3</div>
            <div class="step-text">Choisissez votre mot de passe et finalisez votre inscription</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Avertissement sécurité -->
        <div class="info-box">
          <p>
            <strong>⚠️ Ne partagez jamais ce code.</strong><br>
            AlertProche ne vous demandera jamais votre code par téléphone ou par un autre canal.
            Si vous n'avez pas demandé ce code, ignorez cet email.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          Cet email a été envoyé automatiquement à <strong>{{email}}</strong> suite à une demande d'inscription.<br>
          © 2026 AlertProche — Plateforme Citoyenne de Protection des Personnes Vulnérables.<br>
          Ne répondez pas à cet email.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
